OL,3,CPolice apologise after 'explosive'
OL,4,Creport into treatment of women in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police has said
OL,8,Fsorry and accepted the recommendations
OL,9,Fof an 'explosive' report into the
OL,10,Ftreatment of people arrested and taken
OL,11,Finto custody by the force.
OL,13,FFormer victims' commissioner for
OL,14,FEngland and Wales, Dame Vera Baird KC,
OL,15,Fcarried out the review after being
OL,16,Fasked by Greater Manchester mayor Andy
OL,17,FBurnham, following reports that three
OL,18,Fwomen had accused the force of
OL,19,Funjustified strip searches after being
OL,20,Farrested.
