OL,3,CPolice apologise after 'explosive'
OL,4,Creport into treatment of women in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,8,Fpreviously denied any wrongdoing by
OL,9,Fits staff but, in a statement on
OL,10,FThursday, the force said they "fully
OL,11,Facknowledge" there is "much more to do
OL,12,Faround the cultural practice of strip-
OL,13,Fsearch".
OL,15,FChief Constable Stephen Watson told
OL,16,FITV's Granada Reports that what Dame
OL,17,FVera Baird revealed was "indefensible":
OL,26,@rD@_OUsD@LO]sD@WOUuD@GO]
