OL,3,CPolice apologise after 'explosive'
OL,4,Creport into treatment of women in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FDame Vera's report identified issues
OL,8,Faround GMP's use of arrest, care for
OL,9,Fdomestic and sexual abuse survivors,
OL,10,Ftreatment of women and men in custody,
OL,11,Fuse of strip-search and the handling
OL,12,Fof complaints.
OL,14,FThe force said: "We have apologised
OL,15,Fand accepted the recommendations of an
OL,16,Finquiry into the treatment of people
OL,17,Fin our custody that was commissioned
OL,18,Ffollowing serious allegations in June
OL,19,F2023.
OL,26,@vD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
