OL,7,F"While some improvements to address
OL,8,FDame Vera's recommendations have
OL,9,Falready been made, we fully
OL,10,Facknowledge there is much more to do
OL,11,Faround the cultural practice of strip-
OL,12,Fsearch, particularly for welfare
OL,13,Fpurposes.
OL,15,F"We welcome an opportunity to work
OL,16,Fwith national policing leads to
OL,17,Faccelerate our intention to cease
OL,18,Fstrip-searches for welfare reasons,
OL,19,Fand to improve clarity and scrutiny
OL,20,Faround the grounds of a strip-search.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
