OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FThe force added that they understand
OL,8,Fthe "shock and concern" of members of
OL,9,Fthe public after allegations against
OL,10,Fthe force emerged last summer and said
OL,11,Fthey are "fully committed to doing all
OL,12,Fwe can so the public can have faith in
OL,13,Four protection of women, girls and
OL,14,Fvulnerable people".
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@WO]sD@JOUvD@RO]
