OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FHighlighting changes the force has
OL,8,Falready made, GMP said strip searches
OL,9,Fare "more transparently recorded,
OL,10,Ftightly governed and scrutinised",
OL,11,Fthat every female detainee is
OL,12,Fappointed a dedicated female welfare
OL,13,Fofficer and a centralised standards
OL,14,Fand compliance team now examine
OL,15,Fbetween 150-200 examples of detention
OL,16,Fa month.
OL,18,FThe force also said they are "now
OL,19,F'rooting out' and 'booting out'" staff
OL,20,Fwho are "unfit to wear the uniform".
OL,26,@qD@EOUrD@aO]zD@^OU{D@`O]|D@IOU|D@cO]
