OL,7,FChief Constable Stephen Watson said:
OL,8,F"To those given a voice by this
OL,9,Finquiry who have not received the care
OL,10,Fand consideration they are entitled
OL,11,Fto: I am sorry.
OL,13,F"The issues raised in Dame Vera's
OL,14,Freport speaks to a period when our a
OL,15,Fcustody system under pressure not
OL,16,Fperforming to an acceptable standard.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
