OL,3,CPolice apologise after 'explosive'
OL,4,Creport into treatment of women in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"It evidences poor systems,
OL,8,Fstructures, and incivility,
OL,9,Finsensitivity and compounded by a lack
OL,10,Fof routine leadership, scrutiny, and
OL,11,Findividual examples of low standards,
OL,12,Fpoor behaviour, insensitivity, and a
OL,13,Flack of care in the face of
OL,14,Fvulnerability.
OL,16,F"These issues are of the utmost
OL,17,Fimportance and highlight the need to
OL,18,Fmaintain the highest professional
OL,19,Fstandards.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
