OL,3,CPolice apologise after 'explosive'
OL,4,Creport into treatment of women in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"These must reflect our duty, and
OL,8,Fmoral obligation, to respect and
OL,9,Fuphold the dignity of all detainees
OL,10,Fbut with a particular focus on women
OL,11,Fand girls."
OL,13,FHe added: "We accept the
OL,14,Frecommendations in this report. We
OL,15,Fcommit to implementing them fully and
OL,16,Ffaithfully with a view to making
OL,17,Flasting improvements."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@KO]uD@KOUyD@VO]
