OL,3,CPolice apologise after 'explosive'
OL,4,Creport into treatment of women in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FDame Vera recommended that strip
OL,8,Fsearching should be severely limited,
OL,9,Fproperly regulated and fully recorded,
OL,10,Fand that custody officers should be
OL,11,Freminded of their responsibilities for
OL,12,Fthe accuracy and completeness of
OL,13,Fcustody records.
OL,15,FIn recalling her strip search, a woman
OL,16,Fgiven the name Maria to preserve her
OL,17,Fanonymity, told the inquiry: "The only
OL,18,Freason they did what they did was to
OL,19,Fdegrade me ... If I was a man, I don't
OL,20,Fthink they would've done it. I was
OL,21,Ftreated like a piece of meat."
OL,26,@yD@^OU}D@^O]
