OL,4,Creport into treatment of women in
OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,FDame Vera interviewed more than 15
OL,8,Fpeople who had been arrested and
OL,9,Fdetained by GMP, including three women
OL,10,Ffeatured in a Sky News investigation.
OL,12,FCustody records, detention logs, crime
OL,13,Freports, witness statements and CCTV
OL,14,Ffootage were among documents and data
OL,15,Fthat were trawled through.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
