OL,5,Ccustody
OL,7,F"I understand that the contents of
OL,8,Fthis report will cause further concern
OL,9,Fregarding the treatment of women and
OL,10,Fgirls," he said.
OL,12,F"I want to reassure all women and
OL,13,Fgirls that your safety, trust and
OL,14,Fconfidence remains a priority for the
OL,15,FCollege of Policing, across all of our
OL,16,Fwork."
OL,18,FFormer GMP detective Maggie Oliver
OL,19,Fdescribed the inquiry as "another
OL,20,Fdamning indictment of one of the
OL,21,Fcountry's largest police forces".
