OL,7,FShe said: "Dame Vera Baird's explosive
OL,8,Freport reveals a shocking disregard
OL,9,Ffor rights of those coming into
OL,10,Fcontact with the criminal justice
OL,11,Fsystem."
OL,13,FThe report was commissioned by the
OL,14,FMetro Mayor of Greater Manchester Andy
OL,15,FBurnham.
